Privacy Policy for Babel Bash Chinese

Effective Date: June 1, 2025

Thank you for using Babel Bash Chinese!

Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use the app.

1. No Data Collection
This app does not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive user data. You can use the app without creating an account or providing any personal information.

2. No Internet Access
The app is fully functional offline and does not connect to the internet. It does not send or receive any data in the background.

3. No Ads or In-App Purchases
This app is a one-time purchase and does not contain ads or offer any in-app purchases. Once downloaded, all features are fully available with no additional costs or interruptions.

4. Child and Family Friendly
The app is designed to be safe and appropriate for all ages, including children. It contains only educational content and no inappropriate material.

5. Security
Because the app does not transmit or store any data, there is no risk of your personal information being accessed, leaked, or misused.

6. Changes to This Policy
If this Privacy Policy is updated in the future (for example, due to new features), the revised version will be posted here with an updated "Effective Date."

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
axiomaragames@gmail.com
